Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:42.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会知道 Vajra真正的恐怖之处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:54.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是最新型VF-25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:08.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍摄完成后会用CG加工成VF-0
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡 看见兰歌没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌应该在海角那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是决定穿女装？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:25.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有幸观摩传说中的男旦表演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:29.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转为接受了水下拍摄时的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替男主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是47号镜头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:38.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吻戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:41.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和玛奥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 莫非不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:53.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那打算接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么大不了的 接吻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:05.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑乘坐的车…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 来人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:37.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:47.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:29.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布瑞拉·斯特恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:52.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然被Hydra…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:08.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:16.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:22.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直来救我 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:33.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉眼泪 大家都在看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超究极大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我演玛奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:52.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且想把兰歌的曲子作为主题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:57.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊 这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你演玛奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过禁止采取引人怀疑的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想找回过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别再擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:29.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心搬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没马上答应？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意和阿鲁多接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还没能下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难为她了 情况特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多你自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自己做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:18.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论接吻还是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不了解玛奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:28.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上莎拉姐姐的心上人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:32.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后自己主动献出了吻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没真正恋爱过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:39.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:50.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:54.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过对她来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:24.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 看你紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:28.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己口口声声说接吻没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:37.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:57.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导演 请让我演玛奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛奥的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,47号 镜头11
